<lb n="0865c18"/><head type="no">No. 143 [Nos. 125(51.9), 141-142]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0865c19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>玉耶經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0865c20"/>
<lb n="0865c21"/><byline type="Translator">東晉<note n="0865003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【三】</note><note n="0865003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竺三藏＝西域沙門【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865003"><lem>天竺三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">西域沙門</rdg></app>竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0865c22"/><p>聞如是。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。佛
<lb n="0865c23"/>為四輩弟子說法。時給孤獨家。先為子娶婦
<lb n="0865c24"/><note n="0865004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（得）＋長【三】</note><note n="0865004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（得）＋長【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865004"><lem>長</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">得長</rdg></app>者家女。女名玉耶。端正姝好而生憍慢。
<lb n="0865c25"/>不以婦禮承事<note n="0865005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妐＝翁【宋】，公【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0865005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妐＝翁【宋】，＝公【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0865005"><lem>妐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">翁</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">公</rdg></app>姑夫婿。給孤長者夫妻議
<lb n="0865c26"/>言。子婦不順不<note n="0865006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">依＝從【三】</note><note n="0865006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">依＝從【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865006"><lem>依</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">從</rdg></app>法禮。設加杖捶不欲行
<lb n="0865c27"/>此。置不教訶其過轉增。當如之何。長者<note n="0865007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曰唯＝惟曰【宋】</note><app n="0865007"><lem>曰。
<lb n="0865c28"/>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">惟曰</rdg></app>佛大聖善能化物。<note n="0865008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一切）＋剛【三】</note><note n="0865008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（一切）＋剛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865008"><lem>剛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">一切剛</rdg></app>強弭伏無敢不從。請
<lb n="0865c29"/>佛來化。妻言大善。明<note n="0865009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">旦＝早【三】</note><note n="0865009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">旦＝早【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0865009"><lem>旦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">早</rdg></app>嚴服往詣佛所。頭
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0143.0866a" n="0866a"/>
<lb n="0866a01"/>面著地前白佛言。我家為子娶婦甚大憍慢。
<lb n="0866a02"/>不以<note n="0866001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮節＝婦禮【三】</note><note n="0866001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮節＝婦禮【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866001"><lem>禮節</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婦禮</rdg></app>承事我子。唯願世尊。明日自屈。
<lb n="0866a03"/>將諸弟子到舍中飯。并為玉耶說法。令心開
<lb n="0866a04"/>解改過行善。佛告長者。善哉善哉。給孤長者
<lb n="0866a05"/>聞佛受請歡喜禮佛<note n="0866002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">接＝犍【宋】</note><app n="0866002"><lem>接</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">犍</rdg></app>足而去。歸舍齋戒供
<lb n="0866a06"/>辦中飯。明日佛與千二百五十弟子到長者家。
<lb n="0866a07"/>長者歡喜<note n="0866003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迎＝近【三】</note><note n="0866003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迎＝近【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866003"><lem>迎</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">近</rdg></app>佛作禮。佛坐已定。大小皆出禮
<lb n="0866a08"/>佛&CB00230;住。玉耶逃藏不肯禮佛佛即變化。令長
<lb n="0866a09"/>者家。屋宅牆壁。皆如琉璃水精之色內外相
<lb n="0866a10"/><note n="0866004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝照【明】</note><app n="0866004"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">照</rdg></app>。玉耶<note n="0866005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔見〕－【宋】【元】</note><app n="0866005"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>佛有三十二相八十種好。身<note n="0866006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紫金色＝色紫金【宋】</note><app n="0866006"><lem>紫
<lb n="0866a11"/>金色</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">色紫金</rdg></app>光明<note n="0866007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">暉暉＝煒煒【三】</note><note n="0866007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">暉暉＝煒煒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866007"><lem>暉暉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">煒煒</rdg></app>。玉耶惶怖心驚毛&CB00594;。即出禮
<lb n="0866a12"/>佛頭頂懺悔&CB00230;<note n="0866008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝住【三】</note><note n="0866008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在＝住【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866008"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">住</rdg></app>右面。佛告玉耶。女人不當
<lb n="0866a13"/>自恃端正輕慢夫婿。何謂端正。除<note n="0866009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00230;＝去【三】</note><note n="0866009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00230;＝去【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866009"><lem>&CB00230;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">去</rdg></app>邪態八
<lb n="0866a14"/>十四<note n="0866010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姤＝垢【三】</note><note n="0866010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姤＝垢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866010"><lem>姤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">垢</rdg></app>定意一心是為端正。不以顏色面目
<lb n="0866a15"/>髮綵為端正也。女人身中有十惡事。何等為
<lb n="0866a16"/>十。一者女人初生墮地父母不喜。二者養育
<lb n="0866a17"/>視無滋味。三者女人心常畏人。四者父母&M010527;
<lb n="0866a18"/>憂嫁娶。五者與父母生相離別。六者常畏<note n="0866011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝失【明】</note><app n="0866011"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">失</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866a19"/>婿視其顏色。歡悅輒喜瞋恚則懼。七者懷妊
<lb n="0866a20"/>產生甚難。八者女人小為父母所撿錄。九者
<lb n="0866a21"/>中為夫婿<note n="0866012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所＝禁【三】</note><note n="0866012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">所＝禁【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866012"><lem>所</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">禁</rdg></app>制。十者年老為兒孫所呵。從生
<lb n="0866a22"/>至終不得自在。是為十事。女人不自覺知。玉
<lb n="0866a23"/>耶長跪叉手白佛。稟受<note n="0866013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">賤身＝下賤【三】</note><note n="0866013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">賤身＝下賤【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866013"><lem>賤身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">下賤</rdg></app>不<note n="0866014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">閑＝知【三】</note><note n="0866014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">閑＝知【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866014"><lem>閑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">知</rdg></app>禮儀。唯
<lb n="0866a24"/>願世尊。具說教訓為婦之法。佛告玉耶。婦事
<lb n="0866a25"/><note n="0866015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姑妐＝翁姑【宋】，公姑【元】【明】＊</note><note n="0866015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姑妐＝翁姑【宋】，＝公姑【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0866015"><lem>姑妐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">翁姑</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">公姑</rdg></app>夫婿。有五善三惡。何等為五善。一者
<lb n="0866a26"/>為婦當<note n="0866016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">晚＝後【三】</note><note n="0866016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">晚＝後【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866016"><lem>晚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">後</rdg></app>臥早起。櫛梳髮綵整頓衣服。洗拭
<lb n="0866a27"/>面目勿有垢穢。執於作事先啟所尊。心常恭
<lb n="0866a28"/>順。設有甘美不得先食。二者夫&CB01753;呵罵不得
<lb n="0866a29"/>瞋恨。三者一心守夫婿。不得念邪婬。四者常
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0143.0866b" n="0866b"/>
<lb n="0866b01"/>願夫婿長壽。出行婦當整頓家中。五者常念
<lb n="0866b02"/>夫善不<note n="0866017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念夫＝得念【三】</note><note n="0866017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念夫＝得念【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866017"><lem>念夫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">得念</rdg></app>惡。是為五善。何等為三惡。一
<lb n="0866b03"/>者不以婦禮承事<anchor id="fxT02p0866b01"/>姑妐夫婿。但欲美食先
<lb n="0866b04"/><note n="0866018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝取【三】</note><note n="0866018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝取【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866018"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">取</rdg></app>噉之。未冥早臥日出不起。夫<note n="0866019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲教呵＝若訶教【三】</note><note n="0866019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲教呵＝若訶教【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866019"><lem>欲教呵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">若訶教</rdg></app>瞋
<lb n="0866b05"/>目視夫。應拒<note n="0866020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝獨【三】</note><note n="0866020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猶＝獨【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866020"><lem>猶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">獨</rdg></app>罵。二者不一心向夫婿。但
<lb n="0866b06"/>念他男子。三者欲令夫死早得更嫁。是為三
<lb n="0866b07"/>惡。玉耶默然無辭答佛。佛告玉耶。世間<note n="0866021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（復）＋有【三】</note><note n="0866021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（復）＋有【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866021"><lem>有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">復有</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866b08"/>七輩<note n="0866022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婦＋（何等為七輩）【三】</note><note n="0866022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婦＋（何等為七輩）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866022"><lem>婦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婦何等為七輩</rdg></app>一婦如母。二婦如妹。三婦如善知
<lb n="0866b09"/>識。四婦如婦。五婦如婢。六婦如怨家。七婦如
<lb n="0866b10"/>奪命。是為七輩婦。汝豈<note n="0866023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">解＝能【宋】</note><app n="0866023"><lem>解</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">能</rdg></app>乎。玉耶白佛。不
<lb n="0866b11"/>知七婦盡何所施行。願佛為解之。佛告玉耶。
<lb n="0866b12"/>諦聽諦聽善思念之。吾當為汝分別解說。何
<lb n="0866b13"/>等為母婦母婦者。愛念夫婿猶若慈母。侍其
<lb n="0866b14"/>晨夜不離左右。供養盡心不失時宜。夫若行
<lb n="0866b15"/>來恐人輕易。見則憐念心<note n="0866024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【三】</note><note n="0866024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866024"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>疲厭。憐夫如
<lb n="0866b16"/><note n="0866025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＝母【宋】</note><app n="0866025"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">母</rdg></app>。是為母婦。何等為妹婦。妹婦者。承事夫
<lb n="0866b17"/>婿盡其敬誠。若如兄弟同氣分形。骨肉至親
<lb n="0866b18"/>無有二情。尊奉敬之如妹事兄。是為妹婦。何
<lb n="0866b19"/>等為善知識婦者。侍其夫婿愛念懇至。依依
<lb n="0866b20"/>戀戀不能相棄。私密之事常相告示。見過依
<lb n="0866b21"/>呵令行無失。善事相<note n="0866026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬＝教【三】</note><note n="0866026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敬＝教【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866026"><lem>敬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">教</rdg></app>使益明慧。<note n="0866027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（相親）＋相【三】</note><note n="0866027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（相親）＋相【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866027"><lem>相</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">相親相</rdg></app>愛欲
<lb n="0866b22"/>令度世如善知識。是為善知識婦。何等為婦
<lb n="0866b23"/>婦者。供養大人竭誠盡敬。承事夫婿謙遜順
<lb n="0866b24"/>命。夙興夜寐恭恪言<note n="0866028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝令【三】</note><note n="0866028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命＝令【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866028"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">令</rdg></app>口無逸言身無逸行。
<lb n="0866b25"/>有善推讓過則稱己。誨訓仁施勸進為道。心
<lb n="0866b26"/>端<note n="0866029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">專＝意【三】</note><note n="0866029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">專＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866029"><lem>專</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>一無有<note n="0866030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">分邪精＝邪&CB02510;直【三】</note><note n="0866030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">分邪精＝邪&CB02510;直【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866030"><lem>分邪。精</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">邪&CB02510;直</rdg></app>修婦節終無闕廢。進
<lb n="0866b27"/>不犯儀退不失禮。唯和為貴。是為婦婦。何等
<lb n="0866b28"/>為婢婦者。常懷畏慎不敢自慢。兢兢趣事無
<lb n="0866b29"/>所避憚。心常<note n="0866031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恭恪＝謙恭【三】</note><note n="0866031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恭恪＝謙恭【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866031"><lem>恭恪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">謙恭</rdg></app>忠孝盡節。言以柔軟性常
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0143.0866c" n="0866c"/>
<lb n="0866c01"/>和穆。口不犯&CB00308;邪之<note n="0866032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝語【三】</note><note n="0866032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝語【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866032"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg></app>。身不入放逸之行。
<lb n="0866c02"/>貞良純一質朴直信。&M010527;自嚴整。以禮自將夫
<lb n="0866c03"/>婿。納幸不以憍慢。設不接遇不以為怨。或得
<lb n="0866c04"/>捶杖分受不恚。及見罵辱默而不恨。甘心樂
<lb n="0866c05"/>受無有二意。勸進所好不&CB00107;聲色。遇己曲薄
<lb n="0866c06"/>不訴求直。務修婦節不擇衣食。專精恭恪唯
<lb n="0866c07"/>恐不及。<note n="0866033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">敬奉＝奉敬【三】</note><note n="0866033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">敬奉＝奉敬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866033"><lem>敬奉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">奉敬</rdg></app>夫婿<note n="0866034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如）＋婢【三】</note><note n="0866034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（如）＋婢【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866034"><lem>婢</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">如婢</rdg></app>事大家。是為婢婦。何
<lb n="0866c08"/>等為怨家婦者。見夫不歡&M010527;懷瞋恚。晝夜思
<lb n="0866c09"/>念欲得解離。<note n="0866035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝雖為【三】</note><note n="0866035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＝雖為【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866035"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">雖為</rdg></app>夫婦心常如寄客。狺狺&CB00508;諍
<lb n="0866c10"/>無所畏<note n="0866036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忌＝避【三】</note><note n="0866036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忌＝避【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866036"><lem>忌</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">避</rdg></app>。亂頭墜臥不<note n="0866037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">可＝肯【三】</note><note n="0866037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">可＝肯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866037"><lem>可</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">肯</rdg></app>作使。不念治家
<lb n="0866c11"/>養活兒子。或行婬蕩不知羞恥。<note n="0866038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狀如＝如狀【三】＊</note><note n="0866038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狀如＝如狀【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0866038"><lem>狀如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">如狀</rdg></app>犬畜毀
<lb n="0866c12"/>辱親<note n="0866039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">里＝理【宋】＊</note><app n="0866039"><lem>里</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">理</rdg></app>。譬如怨家。是為怨家婦。何等為奪
<lb n="0866c13"/>命婦者。晝夜不寐<note n="0866040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恚＝毒【三】</note><note n="0866040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恚＝毒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866040"><lem>恚</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">毒</rdg></app>心相向。當何方便得
<lb n="0866c14"/>相遠離。欲與毒藥恐人覺知。或至親<anchor id="fxT02p0866c01"/>里遠
<lb n="0866c15"/>近寄之。作<note n="0866041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝使【三】</note><note n="0866041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝使【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866041"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">使</rdg></app>瞋恚常共賊之。若持寶物雇人
<lb n="0866c16"/>害之。或使傍<note n="0866042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夫＝人【三】</note><note n="0866042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夫＝人【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866042"><lem>夫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">人</rdg></app>伺而殺之。怨&CB00240;夫命。是為
<lb n="0866c17"/>奪命婦。是為七輩婦。玉耶默然。</p>
<lb n="0866c18"/><p>佛告玉耶。五善婦者常有顯名。言行有法眾
<lb n="0866c19"/>人愛敬。宗親九族並蒙其榮。天龍鬼神皆來
<lb n="0866c20"/>擁護使不&CB00240;擴。萬分之後得生天上七寶宮
<lb n="0866c21"/>殿。在所自然侍從左右。壽命延長恣意所<note n="0866043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝之【三】</note><note n="0866043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲＝之【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866043"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>
<lb n="0866c22"/>快樂難言。天上壽盡下生世間。當為富貴<note n="0866044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侯王＝王侯【三】</note><note n="0866044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侯王＝王侯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866044"><lem>侯
<lb n="0866c23"/>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">王侯</rdg></app>子孫。端正聰慧人所奉尊。其<note n="0866045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝二【三】</note><note n="0866045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡＝二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866045"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>婦者常得
<lb n="0866c24"/>惡名。令現在身不得安寧。數為惡鬼眾毒所
<lb n="0866c25"/>病。<note n="0866046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臥起＝起臥【宋】【元】</note><app n="0866046"><lem>臥起</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">起臥</rdg></app>不安惡夢驚怖。所願不得多逢災
<lb n="0866c26"/>撗。萬分之後魂<note n="0866047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝魄【三】</note><note n="0866047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神＝魄【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866047"><lem>神</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">魄</rdg></app>受形。當入地獄餓鬼畜
<lb n="0866c27"/>生。展轉三塗累劫不竟</p>
<lb n="0866c28"/><p>佛告玉耶。是七輩婦汝欲<note n="0866048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行何＝何行【三】</note><note n="0866048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行何＝何行【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0866048"><lem>行何</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">何行</rdg></app>。玉耶流涕前
<lb n="0866c29"/>白佛言。我心愚癡無智所作。自今<note n="0866049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【明】</note><app n="0866049"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>後改往
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0143.0867a" n="0867a"/>
<lb n="0867a01"/>修來。當如婢婦奉事<anchor id="fxT02p0867a01"/>妐姑夫婿。盡我壽命不
<lb n="0867a02"/>敢憍慢。佛告玉耶。善哉善哉。人誰無<note n="0867001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＋（過）【三】</note><note n="0867001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＋（過）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867001"><lem>過</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">過過</rdg></app>能
<lb n="0867a03"/>改者。善莫大焉。玉耶即前請受十戒為優婆
<lb n="0867a04"/>夷。佛告玉耶。持<note n="0867002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一戒＝戒一【三】</note><note n="0867002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一戒＝戒一【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867002"><lem>一戒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">戒一</rdg></app>者不得殺生。二者不
<lb n="0867a05"/>得偷盜取他人<note n="0867003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔財〕－【三】</note><note n="0867003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔財〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867003"><lem>財</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>物。三者不得<note n="0867004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬＋（&CB00105;犯）【宋】＋（泆犯）【元】【明】</note><note n="0867004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬＋（&CB00105;犯）【宋】，＋（泆犯）【元】【明】</note><app n="0867004"><lem>婬</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">婬&CB00105;犯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婬泆犯</rdg></app>他男子。
<lb n="0867a06"/>四者不得<note n="0867005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲酒＝兩舌【三】</note><note n="0867005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲酒＝兩舌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867005"><lem>飲酒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">兩舌</rdg></app>。五者不得<note n="0867006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄語＝飲酒【三】</note><note n="0867006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妄語＝飲酒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867006"><lem>妄語</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">飲酒</rdg></app>。六者不得
<lb n="0867a07"/>惡罵。七者不得綺語。八者不得嫉&CB00107;。九者不
<lb n="0867a08"/>得瞋恚。十者<note n="0867007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當信作＝信【三】</note><note n="0867007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當信作＝信【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867007"><lem>當信作</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">信</rdg></app>善得福作惡得罪。信佛
<lb n="0867a09"/>信法信比丘僧。是為十戒優婆夷法。終身奉
<lb n="0867a10"/>行不敢違犯。佛說經已。諸弟子皆<note n="0867008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔悉〕－【三】</note><note n="0867008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔悉〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867008"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>作禮。
<lb n="0867a11"/>給孤長者<anchor id="fxT02p0867a02"/>姑妐大小及<note n="0867009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔其〕－【三】</note><note n="0867009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867009"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>玉耶。盡行澡水
<lb n="0867a12"/>供養佛百味<note n="0867010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【宋】【元】</note><app n="0867010"><lem>飲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>食。佛告玉耶。當信布施常得
<lb n="0867a13"/>其福。<note n="0867011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔德〕－【三】</note><note n="0867011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔德〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867011"><lem>德</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>後世當復生長者家。玉耶言諾。佛
<lb n="0867a14"/>飯畢<note n="0867012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竟噠＝訖達【三】</note><note n="0867012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竟噠＝訖達【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867012"><lem>竟。噠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">訖達</rdg></app>嚫&CB00057;願。五十善神擁護汝身。佛
<lb n="0867a15"/>告玉<note n="0867013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＋（言）【三】</note><note n="0867013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＋（言）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867013"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">耶言</rdg></app>。勤念經戒。玉耶言。我蒙佛恩得聞
<lb n="0867a16"/>經法。皆前為佛作禮而<note n="0867014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">退＝去【三】</note><note n="0867014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">退＝去【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0867014"><lem>退</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">去</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0867a17"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>玉耶經</jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
